To build and use the application:

 cd centrepoint
 mvn clean install

 This is added content.

After a successful build, the file distribution/target/centrepoint-1.0-SNAPSHOT-bin.zip contains
the full standalone application.

To run, unzip it and run the following command:

 bin/centrepoint console

The application can then be viewed on http://localhost:8080/

